bilingual.source: You might need to add some extra lines.
bilingual.target: 你可能需要添加一些额外的台词。

bilingual.source: "I need extra time and care sometimes, too," Mateo said.
bilingual.target: “有时候我也需要额外的时间和照顾，”马特奥说。

bilingual.source: Try not to put too many extra things on your list.
bilingual.target: 尽量不要在清单上添加太多额外的东西。

bilingual.source: I asked my teacher to give me some extra English homework.
bilingual.target: 我请老师给我一些额外的英语作业。

bilingual.source: Youssef's manager was very happy and he gave Youssef some extra money.
bilingual.target: 优素福的经理非常高兴，并给了优素福一些额外的钱。

bilingual.source: There is extra room inside because the lifts and water pipes are outside.
bilingual.target: 里面有额外的空间，因为电梯和水管都在外面。

bilingual.source: Why don't you walk or cycle to school so that you get some extra exercise?
bilingual.target: 你为什么不步行或骑车上学以获得额外的锻炼呢？
他自愿地承担了额外的工作。
餐厅勤杂工给我们带来了额外的餐巾。

bilingual.source: We need extra chairs for the meeting.
bilingual.target: 我们需要额外的椅子来开会。

list.abstract: extra（英[ˈekstrə]，美[ˈekstrə]），英语单词，作形容词用，为额外的；分外的；外加的。作副词用，为非常；特别地；另外。作名词用，为额外的东西；另外收费的项目；临时演员。短语搭配有extra time（加时赛；延长赛），例句为“It places extra burdens on teachers.（这给教师带来了额外的负担。）” extra副词类近义词有specifically、particularly、badly等，名词类近义词有walker-on、special edition，形容词类近义词有additional、added、excess。
extra是指Extra Web开发平台，由一个框架和众多的基础构件组成。通过Extra构件复用，可提高软件开发商的生产力。

yingyinNormal.en: And they're willing to pay extra to get that particular size onion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们愿意付出额外的金钱。来得到那个完美大小的洋葱。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's go. I got an extra guard duty. Today and I'm on KP this morning. So I can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们走吧。我有额外的执勤，今天上午我得去K.P，以我不能。

yingyinNormal.en: I actually secretly wanted the lockout to continue, because it gave me extra time to get better.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我其实私下里希望这次停摆能继续，因为这给了我额外的时间去提高。

yingyinNormal.en: Most low-wage workers are women. And that extra money would help them pay the bills and provide for their families.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大多数低工资的人是妇女。这些额外的钱将帮助他们付清账单,并供养他们的家人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll have a tall drip, extra hot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要一杯小的现煮咖啡，加热。

yingyinNormal.en: Why didn't you get extra peanut sauce?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你为什么没多加花生酱呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, do you guys have any extra ribbon?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们有多余的缎带吗？

yingyinNormal.en: No, I'm really very extra-sure that I won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我超确定我并不想。

yingyinNormal.en: It gives it that extra edge. You've done us proud.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别有一番风味，我们为你骄傲。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, let's go 2-D. No sense in spending extra money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就看2D场吧。没必要多花钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. So, the usual, with extra spit on Sheldon's hamburger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，惯例，谢尔顿的汉堡上加一口唾沫。

yingyinNormal.en: What's that? Uberweiss. It's new. It's German. It's extra tough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是什么？乌伯怀斯，来自德国的新产品，洗净力超强。

yingyinNormal.en: Extra pineapple slices, extra whipped cream, extra cherries, extra umbrellas, and, hold the rum. Don't let me have too many of those.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多加凤梨片和鲜奶油，再给双份樱桃和小伞，还有，不要朗姆酒。记得别让我喝太多。

yingyinNormal.en: I ordered an extra-large boy with beefy arms, extra guts and glory on the side. This here, this is a talking fishbone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要的是一个手臂粗壮，智勇双全的超大号男生，你给我的是个会说话的鱼骨头。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, pretty lady. Hey, you seem extra happy. I guess I am.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，美女，你看起来格外开心啊。应该是吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, fine. I bought 20 extra tickets for me and Chandler.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好啦，我帮自己跟钱德多买了二十张。

yingyinNormal.en: Who am I? Maya hart. I always give you extra to take home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我呢？玛雅·哈特，我总是多给你点吃的让你带回家。

yingyinNormal.en: And, for extra credit, there's no such thing as time. Time!
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，所谓的时间也是不存在的 给我额外加分吧。时间到！

yingyinNormal.en: Some days I would get there extra early to watch the sunrise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有时我会起个大早，只为去看日出。

yingyinNormal.en: This is an extra copy to have on file. You know, just in case.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是用来存档的另一个副本，你知道的，以防万一。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: added to an existing or usual amount or number

examination_example.sentence: It could make <highlight>extra</highlight> training and instruction affordable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它使人们负担得起额外的培训和指导费用。

examination_example.sentence: Students who do not need the <highlight>extra</highlight> training could cut their debt mountain by a third.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不需要额外培训的学生可以将他们堆积如山的债务削减三分之一。

examination_example.sentence: Therefore, everyone needs to find their <highlight>extra</highlight> — their unique value contribution that makes them stand out in whatever is their field of employment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，每个人都需要找到自己的特别之处——他们独特的价值贡献，使他们在任何就业领域都能脱颖而出。

sense_info_list.en: an item for which an additional charge is made

word_usage.usage: extra作形容词时，可用于名词之前，修饰该名词，如：extra work，也可用于系动词之后，如：Dinner costs 40 yuan , and wine is extra.
extra作形容词时，无比较级和最高级。
